{"tid":1212400,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位手足唔好忘記初衷","createTime":"2019-06-12T18:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T19:01:26.000Z","uid":86632,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"601cfe939eafa5e1c33c276a586c19b534ea7708","tid":1212400,"uid":86632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:28:45.000Z","msg":"冇打算幫警 不過留意到警察嘅行為成為左好多人嘅焦點<br />\n有喺現場有睇live有關注呢件事嘅手足我知你地好嬲 好想啲撚樣死全家<br />\n但希望手足們唔好浪費左100萬人上街呢個咁好嘅勢<br />\n唔好比啲膠層用警察吸晒仇恨<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">記住我地嘅目的係要柒婆撤回惡法</span><br />\n辛苦晒各位義士 記得早啲訓差足電<br />\n聽日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a0a5e53593abafd7f5e1f05187c14418d5d95bd","tid":1212400,"uid":86632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:36:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a24813e93c4c8a064738b4a96fb7aeb96b3e22","tid":1212400,"uid":8265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:01:26.000Z","msg":"推"}]}